title: Dog Does Surprising Thing When Playing On Swings
text:
Dog Does Surprising Thing When Playing On Swings Subscribe to Reshareworthy! It's FREE and always will be! 
This clever dog has found a way to entertain himself in the backyard with this favorite swing set. I couldn’t believe what I was seeing when he twists himself up in the swing and then spins around! He must have watched some kids do it, because it’s exactly what a kid would do to have fun!
